\par }\pard\plain \s60\li-1800\sa180\sl-440\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\tx0\adjustright \b\f16\fs40\up6\cgrid {\f1 KickParticipant Method 
\par }\pard\plain \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\lang1024\cgrid {Kicks a member from the chat room. 
\par }\pard \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i object}{\b .KickParticipant}{ }{\i ParticipantID}{\b ,}{ }{\i KickComment}{\line 
\par }\pard\plain \s61\sb20\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\pvpara\phpg\posy0\absw1560\dxfrtext240\dfrmtxtx240\dfrmtxty240\adjustright \b\f16\fs21\cgrid {\f1 Parts
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i object}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. An object expression that evaluates to a Chat control. 
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i ParticipantID}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. A long integer value that indicates which member will be kicked. If }{\i ParticipantID}{ is set to -1, the method uses the participant ID of the member selected in the Participant list box. If }{\i ParticipantID}{ is not set to -1, the participant ID must have come from an }{\b OnEnterParticipant}{ event. 
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i KickComment}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. A BSTR value that contains a text message with the host's reason for kicking the member. If the kicked member uses the Chat control and has the value 128 (inform about member status changes) set in the }{\b UIOption}{ property, the member will see a message box with this reason. 
\par }\pard\plain \s61\sb20\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\pvpara\phpg\posy0\absw1560\dxfrtext240\dfrmtxtx240\dfrmtxty240\adjustright \b\f16\fs21\cgrid {\f1 Remarks
\par }\pard\plain \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\lang1024\cgrid {This method cannot be called before the }{\b OnEndEnumeration}{ event has been triggered. 
\par }\pard\plain \s88\sa80\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \v\f16\cf5\cgrid {\pard\plain \s88\sa80\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \v\f16\cf5\cgrid {\xe {\v MoveSpitBar Method}}}{\v0\f1 
\par }\pard\plain \s71\li-1770\ri30\sb280\sa250\sl-120\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brdrcf2 \adjustright \fs8\cf8\cgrid {
\par }\pard\plain \s60\li-1800\sa180\sl-440\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\tx0\adjustright \b\f16\fs40\up6\cgrid {\f1 MoveSplitBar Method 
\par }\pard\plain \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\lang1024\cgrid {Changes the appearance of the cursor to a cross hair so the user can resize the control by using the arrow keys or the mouse. 
\par }\pard \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i object}{\b .MoveSplitBar}{\line 
\par }\pard\plain \s61\sb20\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\pvpara\phpg\posy0\absw1560\dxfrtext240\dfrmtxtx240\dfrmtxty240\adjustright \b\f16\fs21\cgrid {\f1 Parts
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i object}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. An object expression that evaluates to a Chat control. 
\par }\pard\plain \s88\sa80\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \v\f16\cf5\cgrid {\pard\plain \s88\sa80\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \v\f16\cf5\cgrid {\xe {\v SelectParticipants Method}}}{\v0\f1 
\par }\pard\plain \s71\li-1770\ri30\sb280\sa250\sl-120\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brdrcf2 \adjustright \fs8\cf8\cgrid {
