\par }\pard\plain \s54\fi-280\li560\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\tx560\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\field\flddirty{\*\fldinst {SYMBOL 183 \\f "Symbol" \\s 9.5 \\h }}{\fldrslt }}{\tab To broadcast the message to all members, the value must be set by an integer, a long integer, or an array of long integers (limited to one element) equal to -1. 
\par }{\field\flddirty{\*\fldinst {SYMBOL 183 \\f "Symbol" \\s 9.5 \\h }}{\fldrslt }}{\tab To whisper to one member (unicast), the value must be set by a long integer equal to the member's participant ID. 
