\par }\pard\plain \s40\qr\sl-160\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs12\cgrid {
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i Count}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. A short integer that determines the number of recipients that will receive the message. To broadcast a message to all members, set the value of }{\i Count}{ to zero. Otherwise, set }{\i Count}{ to the number of members that will receive the message. 
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i Message}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. A VARIANT value that contains the message being distributed: 
