\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. A short integer setting the participant's status changes. Set to zero if the user wants to allow the member to whisper to the user (if }{\i Mask}{ includes 2) or allow the user to receive messages from the member (if }{\i Mask}{ includes 4). Can be set to any combination of the following values. 
\par }\trowd \trleft280 \clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx3160\clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx6960\pard\plain \s85\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \b\fs19\cgrid {Value \cell }\pard\plain \s37\li240\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \b\fs19\cgrid {Description \cell }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\row }\trowd \trleft280 \clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx3160\clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx6960\pard\plain \s82\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {1 \cell }\pard\plain \s38\li240\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {Changes the status of the member to a host. \cell }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\row }\pard\plain \s82\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {2 \cell }\pard\plain \s38\li240\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {Changes the status of the member to a participant. \cell }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\row }\pard\plain \s82\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {4 \cell }\pard\plain \s38\li240\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {Changes the status of the member to a spectator. \cell }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\row }\pard\plain \s82\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {8 \cell }\pard\plain \s38\li240\sb20\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\tx280\tx560\adjustright \fs19\cgrid {Changes the status of the member to not allow whispers. \cell }\pard\plain \nowidctlpar\widctlpar\intbl\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\row }\trowd \trleft280 \clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx3160\clvertalt\cltxlrtb \cellx6960\pard\plain 