\par }\pard \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright {\i object}{\b _OnEndEnumeration}{\line 
\par }\pard\plain \s61\sb20\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\pvpara\phpg\posy0\absw1560\dxfrtext240\dfrmtxtx240\dfrmtxty240\adjustright \b\f16\fs21\cgrid {\f1 Values
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i object}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. An object expression that evaluates to a Chat control. 
\par }\pard\plain \s61\sb20\sl-220\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\pvpara\phpg\posy0\absw1560\dxfrtext240\dfrmtxtx240\dfrmtxty240\adjustright \b\f16\fs21\cgrid {\f1 Remarks
\par }\pard\plain \s116\sa160\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\lang1024\cgrid {The user can start to use the }{\b ThisParticipantID}{ property or the }{\b SetParticipantStatus}{, }{\b KickParticipant}{, }{\b BanParticipant}{, and }{\b SendMessage}{ methods once this event is triggered. 
