\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i object}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {Required. An object expression that evaluates to a Chat control. 
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i ParticipantID}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {A long integer value that contains the participant ID of the member entering the chat room. 
\par }\pard\plain \s64\sl-240\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs21\cgrid {\i Name}{ 
\par }\pard\plain \s65\li280\sa80\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {A BSTR value that contains the alias of the member joining the chat room. 
